i cut down a big overgrown bush and up popped about pink long stemmed lillies did my mother plant these or are they volunteer i was surprised after i spent a whole afternoon and evening cutting an unruley bush out next to my drive i hacked and cut and filled an entire truck bed with limbs and when i pulled up in the drive days later these pretty long stemmed lillies popped up where the bush was cut out my mother died about yrs ago and i keep wondering if all these little surprises came from her or it they are just something that pops up volunteer my boyfriend tells me these are called surprise lillies where do they come from they were planted by your mother what's sweet is the name is lycoris squamigera surprise lily magic lily resurrection lily naked lady in this case i'd call them resurrection lilies since indeed your mother is giving you a gift from the world beyond and living again in memory what a beautiful thing to have happen http davesgarden com pf showimage About a Boy The Shining (film) Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Barbie Sin City The Amber Spyglass Civil engineering and infrastructure repair in New Orleans after Hurricane Katrina Cindy Sheehan Disneyland Flower Shaggy dog story The Family from One End Street Ron Weasley Queen (band) Lilium Beatrice Lillie Avenue Q Eddie Guerrero Wild at Heart (Buffy episode) History of As the World Turns (2000-present) Blood on the Tracks 2003 North America blackout Billboard Hot 100 Smallville (Season 4) AFI 100 Years series Lord Voldemort EastEnders Rose The Ashlee Simpson Show Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an One Tree Hill (TV series) Grandview, U.S.A. Wood carving Toronto Blue Jays U.S. presidential election debates, 2004 Pakistani cricket team in West Indies in 2005 Time Out of Mind C__line Dion Jean Grey The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe Sheryl Crow Jayne Mansfield United Airlines Flight 93 Tenchi Muyo! Blood purity (Harry Potter) Main characters of Fullmetal Alchemist Spice Girls Criticism of governm